#Functions to read mental states
transMat<-function(folder,x) {data.frame(readMat(paste(folder,x,sep = ''))$mat)}
transPW_a<-function(pwRoot,x){
 data.frame(readMat(paste(pwRoot,x,sep = ''))$data.alpha) 
}
transPW_t<-function(pwRoot,x){
 data.frame(readMat(paste(pwRoot,x,sep = ''))$data.theta) 
}

### Reading SSVEP response
transITC_ON<-function(folder,x) {data.frame(readMat(paste(folder,x,sep = ''))$ersp.peaks.ON)}
transITC_OFF<-function(folder,x) {data.frame(readMat(paste(folder,x,sep = ''))$ersp.peaks.OFF)}

transITC_stickness_low<-function(folder,x) {data.frame(readMat(paste(folder,x,sep = ''))$ersp.peaks.stickness.low)}
transITC_stickness_high<-function(folder,x) {data.frame(readMat(paste(folder,x,sep = ''))$ersp.peaks.stickness.high)}

### A super function to combine single trial ERPs and power value in various files for mental states
list2data<-function(filesMat,filesPW,n,subjID) {
    state<-c("EEG_OFF","EEG_ON")
    taskState<-state[n]
    numMat<-grep(pattern = glob2rx(paste(paste(paste(subjID,'_*',sep = ''),taskState,sep = ''),"*",sep = '')),x = filesMat)
    listMat<-filesMat[numMat]
    
    numPW<-grep(pattern = glob2rx(paste(paste(paste(paste("dataComp_",subjID,sep =''),'_*',sep = ''), taskState,sep = ''),"*",sep = '')),x = filesPW)
    listPW<-filesPW[numPW]
## Number of subject
    if (any(grepl("EEG_OFF",listPW))){
        ss1<-7
        ss2<-15
        ss3<-24
        ss4<-29
        } else {
            ss1<-7
            ss2<-15
        ss3<-23
        ss4<-28
        }
    for (i in (1:length(listMat))) {
        if (!exists('dataMat')) {
            dataMat<-transMat(stRoot,listMat[i])#[2:4]
            colnames(dataMat)<-paste(substr(listMat[i],ss1,ss2),c("W","s","t"),sep = '_')
            # colnames(dataMat)[1:2]<-c("t1","t2")
            } else
            {
                tempMat<-transMat(stRoot,listMat[i])
                colnames(tempMat)<-paste(substr(listMat[i],ss1,ss2),c("W","s","t"),sep = '_')
                dataMat<-cbind(dataMat,tempMat)
            }
        }

    for (j in 1:length(listPW)) {
        if (!exists('dataPW_a')) {
            dataPW_a<-transPW_a(pwRoot,listPW[j])
            colnames(dataPW_a)<-paste(paste(substr(listPW[j],ss3,ss4),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"alpha",sep = "_")
            } else
            {
                tempPW_a<-transPW_a(pwRoot,listPW[j])
              colnames(tempPW_a)<-paste(paste(substr(listPW[j],ss3,ss4),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"alpha",sep = "_")
              dataPW_a<-cbind(dataPW_a,tempPW_a)
            }
        }
    for (j in 1:length(listPW)) {
        if (!exists('dataPW_t')) {
            dataPW_t<-transPW_t(pwRoot,listPW[j])
            colnames(dataPW_t)<-paste(paste(substr(listPW[j],ss3,ss4),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"theta",sep = "_")
            } else
            {
                tempPW_t<-transPW_t(pwRoot,listPW[j])
              colnames(tempPW_t)<-paste(paste(substr(listPW[j],ss3,ss4),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"theta",sep = "_")
              dataPW_t<-cbind(dataPW_t,tempPW_t)
            }
    }
    dataState<-cbind(dataMat,cbind(dataPW_a,dataPW_t))
    if (colnames(dataState)[ncol(dataState)] != "Class") {
        dataState[,"Class"]<-character(nrow(dataState))
    }
    dataState["Class"]<-rep(state[n],nrow(dataState))
    dataState[,"Class"] <-ifelse(dataState[,"Class"]=="EEG_OFF","c1","c2")
    return(dataState)
}
### Another super function to combine features for stickiness
list2dataStick<-function(filesMatStick,filesPWStick,m,subjID) {
  ## Stickiness
        stickness<-c("EEG_stickness_low","EEG_stickness_high")
    sticknessState<-stickness[m]
    numMatStick<-grep(pattern = glob2rx(paste(paste(paste(subjID,'_*',sep = ''),sticknessState,sep = ''),"*",sep = '')),x = filesMatStick)
    listMatStick<-filesMatStick[numMatStick]
    numPWStick<-grep(pattern = glob2rx(paste(paste(paste(paste("dataComp_",subjID,sep =''),'_*',sep = ''), sticknessState,sep = ''),"*",sep = '')),x = filesPWStick)
    listPWStick<-filesPWStick[numPWStick]
    ## Stickiness
        if (any(grepl("EEG_stickness_low",listPWStick))){
        ss5<-7
        ss6<-15
        ss7<-34
        ss8<-39
        } else {
        ss5<-7
        ss6<-15
        ss7<-35
        ss8<-40
        }
        for (i in (1:length(listMatStick))) {
        if (!exists('dataMatStick')) {
            dataMatStick<-transMat(stRoot,listMatStick[i])#[2:4]
            colnames(dataMatStick)<-paste(substr(listMatStick[i],ss5,ss6),c("W","s","t"),sep = '_')
            # colnames(dataMat)[1:2]<-c("t1","t2")
            } else
            {
                tempMatStick<-transMat(stRoot,listMatStick[i])
                colnames(tempMatStick)<-paste(substr(listMatStick[i],ss5,ss6),c("W","s","t"),sep = '_')
                dataMatStick<-cbind(dataMatStick,tempMatStick)
            }
        }

    for (j in 1:length(listPWStick)) {
        if (!exists('dataPW_aStick')) {
            dataPW_aStick<-transPW_a(pwRoot,listPWStick[j])
            colnames(dataPW_aStick)<-paste(paste(substr(listPWStick[j],ss7,ss8),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"alpha",sep = "_")
            } else
            {
                tempPW_aStick<-transPW_a(pwRoot,listPWStick[j])
              colnames(tempPW_aStick)<-paste(paste(substr(listPWStick[j],ss7,ss8),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"alpha",sep = "_")
              dataPW_aStick<-cbind(dataPW_aStick,tempPW_aStick)
            }
        }
    for (j in 1:length(listPWStick)) {
        if (!exists('dataPW_tStick')) {
            dataPW_tStick<-transPW_t(pwRoot,listPWStick[j])
            colnames(dataPW_tStick)<-paste(paste(substr(listPWStick[j],ss7,ss8),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"theta",sep = "_")
          # colnames(dataPW_t)[1:2]<-c("t1","t2")
            } else
            {
                tempPW_tStick<-transPW_t(pwRoot,listPWStick[j])
              colnames(tempPW_tStick)<-paste(paste(substr(listPWStick[j],ss7,ss8),c("pre","post"),sep = '_'),"theta",sep = "_")
              dataPW_tStick<-cbind(dataPW_tStick,tempPW_tStick)
            }
    }
    dataStick<-cbind(dataMatStick,cbind(dataPW_aStick,dataPW_tStick))
    if (colnames(dataStick)[ncol(dataStick)] != "Class") {
        dataStick[,"Class"]<-character(nrow(dataStick))
    }
    dataStick["Class"]<-rep(sticknessState,nrow(dataStick))
    dataStick[,"Class"] <-ifelse(dataStick[,"Class"]=="EEG_stickness_low","c1","c2")
    return(dataStick)
}

## Functions to sample and split the datasets
## Normalization
normVar<-function(dSART){
  normDat<-data.frame(scale(dSART[setdiff(colnames(dSART),"Class")]),dSART$Class)
  colnames(normDat)[ncol(normDat)]<-"Class"
  return(normDat)
}
samTrain<-function(seed,dataSART_MW){
  set.seed(seed)
  smp_size <- floor(0.7 * nrow(dataSART_MW))
  train_ind <- sample(seq_len(nrow(dataSART_MW)), size = smp_size)
    # test <- dataSART_MW[-train_ind, ]
  train_SART <- dataSART_MW[train_ind, ]
  train_SART[,"Class"]<-as.factor(train_SART[,"Class"])
  return(train_SART)
}
samTest<-function(seed,dataSART_MW){
  set.seed(seed)
  smp_size <- floor(0.7 * nrow(dataSART_MW))
  train_ind <- sample(seq_len(nrow(dataSART_MW)), size = smp_size)
  test_SART <- dataSART_MW[-train_ind, ]
  test_SART[,"Class"]<-as.factor(test_SART[,"Class"])
  return(test_SART)
}
tNosplit_train<-function(seed,tNoSART_MW){
  set.seed(seed)
  smp_size <- floor(0.7 * length(tNoSART_MW))
  train_ind <- sample(seq_len(length(tNoSART_MW)), size = smp_size)
  tNoSART_MW_train<-tNoSART_MW[train_ind]
  return(tNoSART_MW_train)
}
tNosplit_test<-function(seed,tNoSART_MW){
  set.seed(seed)
  smp_size <- floor(0.7 * length(tNoSART_MW))
  train_ind <- sample(seq_len(length(tNoSART_MW)), size = smp_size)
  tNoSART_MW_test<-tNoSART_MW[-train_ind]
  return(tNoSART_MW_test)
}

sepTrain <- function(seed,dSART){
    set.seed(seed)
    classes<-dSART[,"Class"]
    train_set_SART <- createDataPartition(classes, p = 0.7, list = FALSE)
    train_SART<-dSART[train_set_SART,]
    train_SART[,"Class"]<-as.factor(train_SART[,"Class"])
    return(train_SART)
 }
sepTest <- function(seed,dSART){
    set.seed(seed)
    classes<-dSART[,"Class"]
    train_set_SART <- createDataPartition(classes, p = 0.7, list = FALSE)
    test_SART<-dSART[-train_set_SART,]
    test_SART[,"Class"]<-as.factor(test_SART[,"Class"])
    return(test_SART)
}
subSam<-function(dSART){
  upSample(x = dSART[,-ncol(dSART)],y = dSART$Class)
}

#### Calculate the accuracy of the model given the dataset
accPfm<-function(ReMod,train_SART) {
  tabLM.train<-table(Actual =train_SART$Class, Predicted = ifelse(predict(ReMod,train_SART,type =
                                                                            "prob")[,1]>0.5,"c1","c2"))
  # tabLM.train
  accTrain<-sum(diag(tabLM.train))/sum(tabLM.train)
  senTrain<-tabLM.train[1,1]/sum(tabLM.train[1,])
  speTrain<-tabLM.train[2,2]/sum(tabLM.train[2,])
  statTrain<-c(accTrain,senTrain,speTrain)
  return(statTrain)
}

accPfmResp<-function(modSVM_SART,train_SART.SVM) {
  tabLM.train<-table(Actual =train_SART.SVM$Class, Predicted = predict(modSVM_SART,train_SART.SVM,type = "raw"))
  accTrain<-sum(diag(tabLM.train))/sum(tabLM.train)
  senTrain<-tabLM.train[1,1]/sum(tabLM.train[1,])
  speTrain<-tabLM.train[2,2]/sum(tabLM.train[2,])
  statTrain<-c(accTrain,senTrain,speTrain)
  return(statTrain)
}

  meandataSART_Stickv2<-sumdataSART_Stickv2 %>%
    gather(key = variables,factor_key = "variables",value = "val",-Class) %>%
   group_by(Class,variables) %>%
     summarise(meanVal = mean(val))
  write.csv(sumdataSART_Stickv2,file = paste(feaRoot,paste(paste("sumdataSART_Stickv2",subjID,sep = '_'),".csv",sep =""),sep =''))
  write.csv(meandataSART_Stickv2,file = paste(feaRoot,paste(paste("meandataSART_Stickv2",subjID,sep = '_'),".csv",sep =""),sep =''))
  
  tNoSART_StickLowv2<-1:nrow(dataSART_StickLowv2)
  tNoSART_StickHighv2<-1:nrow(dataSART_StickHighv2)
  pctSART_Stick[[subjID]]<-nrow(dataSART_StickLow)/(nrow(dataSART_StickLow)+nrow(dataSART_StickHigh))
  pctSART_Stickv2[[subjID]]<-nrow(dataSART_StickLowv2)/(nrow(dataSART_StickLowv2)+nrow(dataSART_StickHighv2))
  
  
  #### Stickiness resampling
  #### SART task: normalized or original data:train_subsam or test
  SART_StickLow_train<-samTrain(seed,dataSART_StickLow)
  SART_StickLow_test<-samTest(seed,dataSART_StickLow)
  tNoSART_StickLow_train<-tNosplit_train(seed,tNoSART_StickLow)
  tNoSART_StickLow_test<-tNosplit_test(seed,tNoSART_StickLow)
  
  SART_StickHigh_train<-samTrain(seed,dataSART_StickHigh)
  SART_StickHigh_test<-samTest(seed,dataSART_StickHigh)
  tNoSART_StickHigh_train<-tNosplit_train(seed,tNoSART_StickHigh)
  tNoSART_StickHigh_test<-tNosplit_test(seed,tNoSART_StickHigh)
  ### Recombine the datasets
  rbSART_Stick_train<-rbind(SART_StickLow_train,SART_StickHigh_train)

  
  dSART_Stick.o_test<-rbind(SART_StickLow_test,SART_StickHigh_test)
  dSART_Stick.o_test$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stick.o_test$Class)
  dSART_Stick.o_subsam<-rbSART_Stick_train 
  dSART_Stick.o_subsam$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stick.o_subsam$Class)
  
  dSART_Stick_subsam<-normVar(rbSART_Stick_train)
  dSART_Stick_subsam$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stick_subsam$Class)
  dSART_Stick_test<-normVar(rbind(SART_StickLow_test,SART_StickHigh_test))
  dSART_Stick_test$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stick_test$Class)
  
  tNoSART_Stick_train<-rbind(tNoSART_StickLow_train,tNoSART_StickHigh_train)
  tNoSART_Stick_test<-rbind(tNoSART_StickLow_test,tNoSART_StickHigh_test)
  
  
  
  #### SART task v2 with ERSP added: normalized or original data:train_subsam or test
  SART_StickLowv2_train<-samTrain(seed,dataSART_StickLowv2)
  SART_StickLowv2_test<-samTest(seed,dataSART_StickLowv2)
  tNoSART_StickLowv2_train<-tNosplit_train(seed,tNoSART_StickLowv2)
  tNoSART_StickLowv2_test<-tNosplit_test(seed,tNoSART_StickLowv2)
  #
  SART_StickHighv2_train<-samTrain(seed,dataSART_StickHighv2)
  SART_StickHighv2_test<-samTest(seed,dataSART_StickHighv2)
  tNoSART_StickHighv2_train<-tNosplit_train(seed,tNoSART_StickHighv2)
  tNoSART_StickHighv2_test<-tNosplit_test(seed,tNoSART_StickHighv2)
  #
  rbSARTv2_train<-rbind(SART_StickLowv2_train,SART_StickHighv2_train)
  
  #
  dSART_Stickv2.o_test<-rbind(SART_StickLowv2_test,SART_StickHighv2_test)
  dSART_Stickv2.o_test$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stickv2.o_test$Class)
  dSART_Stickv2.o_subsam<-rbSARTv2_train
  dSART_Stickv2.o_subsam$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stickv2.o_subsam$Class)
  #
  dSART_Stickv2_subsam<-normVar(rbSARTv2_train)
  dSART_Stickv2_subsam$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stickv2_subsam$Class)
  dSART_Stickv2_test<-normVar(rbind(SART_StickLowv2_test,SART_StickHighv2_test))
  dSART_Stickv2_test$Class<-as.factor(dSART_Stickv2_test$Class)
  tNoSART_Stickv2_train<-rbind(tNoSART_StickLowv2_train,tNoSART_StickHighv2_train)
  tNoSART_Stickv2_test<-rbind(tNoSART_StickLowv2_test,tNoSART_StickHighv2_test)
  
  ## Confusion matrix
  accPfm<-function(ReMod,train_SART) {
    tabLM.train<-table(Actual =train_SART$Class, Predicted = ifelse(predict(ReMod,train_SART,type =
                                                                              "prob")[,1]>0.5,"c1","c2"
                                                                    )
                       )
    # tabLM.train
    accTrain<-sum(diag(tabLM.train))/sum(tabLM.train)
    senTrain<-tabLM.train[1,1]/sum(tabLM.train[1,])
    speTrain<-tabLM.train[2,2]/sum(tabLM.train[2,])
    statTrain<-c(accTrain,senTrain,speTrain)
  return(statTrain)
    # return(accTrain)
  }
  ## SVM
  svm_ctrl <- trainControl(method = "cv", number = 10,classProbs =  TRUE,
                            verboseIter = FALSE
                           ,sampling = "up"
                           )
  svmgrid<-expand.grid(sigma = 10^(-5:-1),
                       C = 10^(-3:1)
                         )
  modSVM_SART_Stick <- train(Class ~ ., data = dSART_Stick_subsam,
    method = "svmRadial",
                      # preProcess = c("center"),
                      tuneGrid = svmgrid,
                      tuneLength = 9,
                      trControl = svm_ctrl)
  summary(modSVM_SART_Stick)
  # modSVM_SART_Stick.f<-modSVM_SART_Stick$finalModel
  
  accSART_StickSVM_train<-rbind(accSART_StickSVM_train,accPfmResp(modSVM_SART_Stick,dSART_Stick_subsam))
  accSART_StickSVM_test<-rbind(accSART_StickSVM_test,accPfmResp(modSVM_SART_Stick,dSART_Stick_test))
  
  dSART_Stick4v<-rbind(dSART_Stick_subsam,dSART_Stick_test) %>%
    gather(key = variables,factor_key = "variables",value = "val",-Class)
  pctMW_act_SART_Stick<-table(dSART_Stick4v$Class)[1]/sum(table(dSART_Stick4v$Class))
  plt_dist_SART_Stick<-ggplot(data = dSART_Stick4v,mapping = aes(x = variables,y = val,color = Class))+
    geom_boxplot(outlier.shape =3,outlier.size = .8,size = 1)+
    geom_jitter(alpha = 0.4)+
    annotate("text",label = round(pctMW_act_SART_Stick,2),x = 5, y = 10,size = 15,color = "grey")+
    scale_color_discrete(labels = c("MW","OT"))+
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(colour="black",angle=90,hjust=.5,vjust=0))
  ggsave(filename = paste(pltRoot,paste("SARTSVM_dist_",paste(subjID,".pdf",sep = ''),sep = ''),sep = ''),plot = plt_dist_SART_Stick,width = 16,height = 12)
  
  probSART_StickSVM_test[subjID]<-predict(modSVM_SART_Stick,dSART_Stick_test,type = "prob")
  probSART_StickSVM_train[subjID]<-predict(modSVM_SART_Stick,dSART_Stick_subsam,type = "prob")
  # cbind(tNoSART_train,data.frame(probSARTSVM_train[[2]]))
  probSART_StickSVM[[subjID]]<-cbind(set =  c(rep("train",nrow(dSART_Stick_subsam)),rep("test",nrow(dSART_Stick_test))),prob = predict(modSVM_SART_Stick,rbind(dSART_Stick_subsam,dSART_Stick_test),type = "prob"))
  pbSART_StickSVM_gp<-data.frame(data.frame(ifelse(probSART_StickSVM[[subjID]]$prob.c1>0.5,"MW","OT")),probSART_StickSVM[[subjID]]$prob.c1)
  colnames(pbSART_StickSVM_gp)<-c("stim","probs")
  pctMW_hist_SART_Stick<-table(pbSART_StickSVM_gp$stim)[1]/sum(table(pbSART_StickSVM_gp$stim))
  p1<-ggplot(data = pbSART_StickSVM_gp,aes(x = probs,group = stim,fill = stim))+
    geom_histogram(size = 1,bins = 50,position = "dodge")+
    geom_vline(xintercept = 0.5,color = "grey",size = 1,linetype = 2)+
    annotate("text",label = round(pctMW_hist_SART_Stick,2),x = .5, y = 100,size = 10,color = "grey")+
    coord_cartesian(xlim=c(0,1))
  ggsave(filename = paste(pltRoot,paste("SART_StickSVM_",paste(subjID,".pdf",sep = ''),sep = ''),sep = ''),plot = p1,width = 9,height = 6)

  ## SVM for stickiness in SART with SSVEP response 
  modSVM_SART_Stickv2 <- train(factor(Class) ~ ., data = dSART_Stickv2_subsam,
    method = "svmRadial",
                      # preProcess = c("center"),
                      tuneGrid = svmgrid,
                      tuneLength = 9,
                      trControl = svm_ctrl)
  accSART_Stickv2SVM_train<-rbind(accSART_Stickv2SVM_train,accPfmResp(modSVM_SART_Stickv2,dSART_Stickv2_subsam))
  accSART_Stickv2SVM_test<-rbind(accSART_Stickv2SVM_test,accPfmResp(modSVM_SART_Stickv2,dSART_Stickv2_test))
  dSART_Stickv24v<-rbind(dSART_Stickv2_subsam,dSART_Stickv2_test) %>%
    gather(key = variables,factor_key = "variables",value = "val",-Class)
  pctMW_act_SART_Stickv2<-table(dSART_Stickv24v$Class)[1]/sum(table(dSART_Stickv24v$Class))
  plt_dist_SART_Stickv2<-ggplot(data = dSART_Stickv24v,mapping = aes(x = variables,y = val,color = Class))+
    geom_boxplot(outlier.shape =3,outlier.size = .8,size = 1)+
    geom_jitter(alpha = 0.4)+
    annotate("text",label = round(pctMW_act_SART_Stickv2,2),x = 5, y = 10,size = 15,color = "grey")+
    scale_color_discrete(labels = c("MW","OT"))+
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(colour="black",angle=90,hjust=.5,vjust=0))
  ggsave(filename = paste(pltRoot,paste("SART_Stickv2SVM_dist_",paste(subjID,".pdf",sep = ''),sep = ''),sep = ''),plot = plt_dist_SART_Stickv2,width = 16,height = 12)
  
  
  probSART_Stickv2SVM_test[subjID]<-predict(modSVM_SART_Stickv2,dSART_Stickv2_test,type = "prob")
  probSART_Stickv2SVM_train[subjID]<-predict(modSVM_SART_Stickv2,dSART_Stickv2_subsam,type = "prob")
  probSART_Stickv2SVM[[subjID]]<-cbind(set =c(rep("train",nrow(dSART_Stickv2_subsam)),rep("test",nrow(dSART_Stickv2_test))),predict(modSVM_SART_Stickv2,rbind(dSART_Stickv2_subsam,dSART_Stickv2_test),type = "prob"))
  pbSART_Stickv2SVM_gp<-data.frame(data.frame(ifelse(probSART_Stickv2SVM[[subjID]]$c1>0.5,"MW","OT")),probSART_Stickv2SVM[[subjID]]$c1)
  colnames(pbSART_Stickv2SVM_gp)<-c("stim","probs")
  pctMW_hist_SART_Stickv2<-table(pbSART_Stickv2SVM_gp$stim)[1]/sum(table(pbSART_Stickv2SVM_gp$stim))
  p2<-ggplot(data = pbSART_Stickv2SVM_gp,aes(x = probs,group = stim,fill = stim))+
    geom_histogram(size = 1,bins = 50,position = "dodge")+
    geom_vline(xintercept = 0.5,color = "grey",size = 1,linetype = 2)+
    annotate("text",label = round(pctMW_hist_SART_Stickv2,2),x = .5, y = 100,size = 10,color = "grey")+
    coord_cartesian(xlim=c(0,1))
  ggsave(filename = paste(pltRoot,paste("SART_Stickv2SVM_",paste(subjID,".pdf",sep = ''),sep = ''),sep = ''),plot = p2,width = 9,height = 6)

listMean<-list.files(feaRoot,pattern = glob2rx(paste("meandataSART_v2","*.csv",sep = "")))
transMean<-function(feaRoot,x){
 data.frame(read.csv(paste(feaRoot,x,sep = ''),header = TRUE,row.names = "X")) 
}
## mean value for each subject
    for (i in (1:length(listMean))) {
        if (!exists('dataMean')) {
            dataMean<-transMean(feaRoot,listMean[i])#[2:4]
            dataMean[,"subjID"]<-rep(unlist(strsplit((strsplit(listMean[i],'_')[[1]][3]),'.csv')),nrow(dataMean))
            } else
            {
                tempMean<-transMean(feaRoot,listMean[i])
                tempMean[,"subjID"]<-rep(unlist(strsplit((strsplit(listMean[i],'_')[[1]][3]),'.csv')),nrow(tempMean))
                dataMean<-rbind(dataMean,tempMean)
            }
    }
